    "synopsis": "The Fallen Dome of Periculus has been found again, and every noble, Guilder and hive-scum faction with a taste for profit wants what lies inside. Tempes Sol of the Guild of Light sees the dome as a weapon against Lord Silas Pureburn, a Redemptionist firebrand with the Underhive at his back, but the expeditions uncover more than loot: forbidden archeotech, flesh-hungry things and a rage that spreads through everyone it touches. Denny Flowers turns the treasure hunt into Necromunda archeotech horror, with religious violence burning under the skin.",
